<br>
First off, dual wielding will be your best bet with not having a haste item. Try and find a Venomous Axe of the Velium Brood and another cheap proccing weapon. I always liked my Blood point in secondary at lower levels for the 80 pt lifetap. Helps with heals. <br>
<br>
Secondly, get yourself a decent BP. Ry'Gorr Battle Mail is decent, but if you're willing to spare the cash, a Barbed Ringmail would be your best bet til you get some Thurg armor. As for your range, keep your bow, if you can, try and find yourself a cheap nightmarewood compound (usually around 1k on E'Ci). Rings, Velium Fire Wedding Rings are #1 for warriors, period. Until you can afford Vallorium (5k each on E'Ci). <br>
<br>
Third, get yourself a Cloak of the Maelstrom. heavy, but worth the AC/HP and stats. (usually 2k or less on E'Ci). Otherwise, spider fur is nice. Also look for spider fur collar and belt (unless you're getting a haste belt). If the haste belt's the case, FBSS is a good starter belt. I myself bought a pair of Silver Chitin Hand Wraps and got a spider fur belt. Better stats for AC/HP. <br>
<br>
Those are the basics I would look for. If you see any items you're questioning, use this basic formula to figure out the value of the item to a warrior:<br>
<br>
CV (Combat Value) = overall value of an item taken by adding the individual values of your stats.<br>
<br>
1 CV = 1 AC = 2 STR = 2 STA = 10 HP = 5 Agi = 3 DEX = 3 SVM = 4 SVF = 4 SVC = 6 SVD = 6 SVP<br>
<br>
Int, Wis, and Cha are pretty much worthless for warriors aside from tradeskilling and selling/buying from vendors. <br>
<br>
Basically, if item (A) has 10 AC, 5 STR, 25 HP and item (B) has AC 5, 5 Agi, 5 Dex, 15 HP; you compare the items by adding the CV. <br>
<br>
(A) 10 AC + (5 STR/2) + (25 HP/10) = 15 CV<br>
(B) 5 AC + (5 Agi/5) + (5 Dex/3) + (15 HP/10) = 9 CV<br>
<br>
So item (A) is better for you.<br>
<br>
If you can understand that, you're set. Good Luck!  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=angelcrusha>AngelCrusha</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.strike9.com/file.aspx?path=/Angelcrusha/thumbnails/Rude+1+Avatar.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 9/17/03 3:23 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=5572.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=5572.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=5572.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=5572.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5572.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5572.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form